Comment: 10,0:00:15.50,0:00:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.08,0:00:22.00,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The end draws near for Satoshi and his friends’ \N research projects on Poni Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.00,0:00:25.80,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,It seems Hāpu'u came to see them \N at the Pokémon Center today.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.13,0:00:27.26,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Why, is this not...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.80,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,A Flying-Z!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.80,0:00:32.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kaki’s new Z-Move was so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.56,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I wish I got to see it, too! \N Your, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.56,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Final Dive Crash! \N Yesterday, I surpassed myself! {"ore o koeta", so it should remain "surpassed" like in last episode's title, right? Noting it here in case 107's title gets changed for some reason. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.94,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Does this mean you have conquered \N Kapu-Rehire’s Trial?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.94,0:00:47.11,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I wish dearly that I may be \N accepted as Island Queen soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.95,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It’s all thanks to my grandfather.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.95,0:00:49.78,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Grandfather?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.45,0:00:52.87,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,During my battle with Kapu-Tetefu,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.87,0:00:55.29,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,I recalled my late grandfather’s words.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.12,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,And then our power welled up...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.25,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Sandy, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.75,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Togedemaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:07.59,0:01:08.80,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,This old man... Kaki!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.06,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Look, it’s the guy we met yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.06,0:01:23.06,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You’re right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.48,0:01:25.44,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Is my grandfather familiar to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.90,0:01:28.82,Main,Kaki & Satoshi,0,0,0,,“My grandfather”?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.82,0:01:31.53,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,You mean the Island King \N before the last one-roto?! {Kinda wanna suggest "You mean the penultimate Island King-roto?!". - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.62,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,No, look, we met this guy {\i1}yesterday!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.62,0:01:39.37,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Can’t it have been someone else? \N I mean, Hāpu'u’s grandfather is already...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.79,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,But I {\i1}know{\i0} it was this old guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.04,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,He was doing crazy well, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.59,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,That must be Kapu-Rehire’s power.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.42,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,The Guardian Deity at the Ruins of Paradise, \N Kapu-Rehire...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.42,0:01:54.64,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,...possesses the mystical power to grant the living \N audience with those who have passed.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.22,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,So it was true...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.85,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,My brother, Gladio, said that his reason \N for coming to meet Kapu-Rehire...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.15,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,...was to meet our departed father.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.73,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.27,0:02:13.24,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u, do you believe that Kapu-Rehire \N will let us meet our father?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.24,0:02:16.28,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I very well understand \N how you feel...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.20,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,But you must be cautious.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.20,0:02:22.37,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Some have found themselves unable to return \N from the world within Kapu-Rehire’s mist,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.58,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,where this world and the next intersect.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.38,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,When they finally reunite \N with those they wish to meet,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.38,0:02:31.34,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,the inevitable second parting to be faced \N becomes all the more painful.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.38,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,The ones who cannot \N endure this pain...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.38,0:02:36.51,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,...will be forever trapped \N within the mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.72,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Sorry, I... I’m just going \N outside for a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.60,0:02:45.85,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Did Mao have someone, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.82,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Back when Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan} was little, \N Maomama fell ill, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.53,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.78,0:02:55.82,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,It’s all right. {For the record, I didn't RULE BREAKER this. I feel tempted to at least give it more lead-in, but I'll let you decide. - Toa}{Trying to RULE BREAKER it to ignore the keyframe and... I think it works? -Starfish}
