Comment: 10,0:04:28.50,0:04:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.56,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan}, do you want to see Maomama?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.23,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,I’m sure you do...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.73,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I don’t!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.65,0:04:55.53,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.49,0:05:05.62,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’ve been looking forward \N to taking this walk for so long!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.00,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry I haven’t been \N able to go with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.00,0:05:12.50,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You didn’t have a choice. \N You were in the hospital, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.75,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for getting sick...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.30,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Don’t be sorry! I get sick, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.30,0:05:22.39,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s right! I got a cold not too long ago, \N and went to the hospital with Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.18,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I know. Your father told me.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.18,0:05:28.81,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I’m so proud of you! He told me \N you can finally take your own medicine, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.14,0:05:30.06,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.64,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.64,0:05:33.81,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I wish I could have been there for you \N when you had a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.61,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom, look! \N It’s a Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.61,0:05:41.03,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,That one is called Amakaji.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.45,0:05:43.32,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,It’s so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.74,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Shall we catch it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.74,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,We can do that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.95,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Perhaps, if we’re lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.79,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,A Monster Ball!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.67,0:05:53.25,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.67,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.84,0:06:01.67,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,We got it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.97,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,We’re so...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.43,Main,Mao & Maomama,0,0,0,,...lucky today!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.39,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Pleasure to meet you, Amakaji.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.15,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.31,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,She’s my...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.98,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,...little sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.52,0:06:20.69,Main,Mao & Maomama,0,0,0,,Oh, your little sister?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.69,0:06:24.95,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Not too long after that, \N she had to go to the hospital again...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.28,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Every time I went to go see her, \N she’d apologize more and more...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.62,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,“I’m sorry,” \N was just about all she’d say...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.62,0:06:34.21,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I didn’t like that side of her...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.79,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I mean, it wasn’t {\i1}her{\i0} fault \N that she was sick...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.34,0:06:43.01,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Now, I feel like I finally \N understand how she felt...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.72,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.22,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,But back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.97,0:06:52.18,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,All you ever say is “I’m sorry” this \N and “I’m sorry” that... I hate you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.18,0:06:52.93,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.69,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.40,0:07:01.94,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That ended up being \N the last time I ever spoke to her...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.03,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I don’t want to see her...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.95,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I can’t, not after I was \N so cruel to her...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.30,0:07:26.22,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,It has been a very long time \N since having so many guests stay over.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.22,0:07:27.84,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,This is quite exciting!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.30,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,We’re happy to be here!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.77,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Amajo. \N Did I make you worry?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.02,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Sorry to all of you, too. {Manually extended this line (a reversal from my usual use of RULE BREAKER!) since I thought it was too short. It originally cut off at the keyframe. Consequently cut down the lead-in for the next line, which has just around 100-ish ms instead now. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.02,0:07:38.77,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Oh, it is nothing to fret about.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.77,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,That’s right!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.69,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.11,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Hey, what sort of games \N will we play at your house?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.11,0:07:47.11,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Playing games will have to wait until after \N we’ve helped her plant the Poni Radish seeds.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.61,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Oh, of course...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.42,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,May you grow into \N excellent Poni Radishes!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.09,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,And the next assignment is...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.61,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I can’t believe she does this \N on her own all the time...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.82,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u is incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.61,Main,Class,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.04,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Silvuddy! Air Slash! {RULE BREAKER! - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.67,0:08:41.29,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Lugarugan! Stone Edge! {RULE BREAKER! x2 - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.81,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Could this perhaps be... \N Kapu-Rehire’s mist?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.22,0:08:58.39,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Are you all there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.44,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Heed my call!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.90,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.69,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,I’m over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.40,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Don’t move! \N We’re coming to you! {Fixed casing. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.15,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,The weather was so nice \N until just now...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.15,0:09:10.86,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,This is just like the mist \N from yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.16,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Where are the rest?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.53,0:09:18.16,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Mao! Lilie! Satoshi! Can you hear my voice?! \N Respond to my call!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.04,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Kaki! Māmane!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.09,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.67,0:09:33.39,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Where are you, everybody?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.22,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Mao!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.85,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Suiren!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.77,0:09:45.44,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,This is odd... The field outside of Hāpu'u’s house \N wasn’t this big, was it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.44,0:09:49.94,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness... \N I was afraid I’d gotten lost in the mist!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.32,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Lilie?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.37,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Big Brother! \N What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.91,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,I could ask you the same... \N What are you doing in this forest?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.91,0:10:00.37,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Forest? I thought \N I was at Hāpu'u’s house...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.37,0:10:03.50,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,I had gone to visit Hāpu'u \N with the others!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.33,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.09,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Is this Kapu-Rehire’s mist?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.01,0:10:10.97,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.97,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.59,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Lilie, where are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.85,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,They have been trapped \N within Kapu-Rehire’s mist.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.23,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,The world within Kapu-Rehire’s mist...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.23,0:10:24.35,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,...is a mystical place where \N our world and the next intersect.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.35,0:10:28.77,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Mao and the others could be near, \N yet at the same time beyond our reach.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.32,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Somewhere they may reunite with one \N who has departed this world...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.74,0:10:35.95,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Lilie said she wanted to see \N her father, didn’t she?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.99,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,And Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan} must have wanted \N to see Maomama!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.54,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Then, what about Satoshi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.54,0:10:42.83,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Does Satoshi have somebody \N he wants to meet in this mist, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.46,0:10:50.92,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Wait, Nyaheat! \N Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.47,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What’s wrong?
Comment: 10,0:11:03.48,0:11:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.40,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,I’ll get Pokémon!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.36,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mooland?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.00,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}is{\i0} Mooland!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.38,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,I don’t believe it-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.30,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,It’s been so long, Mooland!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.35,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Well, doesn’t matter how. \N You got to see Mooland, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.27,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Right, Nyaheat?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.53,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Fire Fang-roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.20,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Now a Nitro Charge-roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.62,0:12:06.79,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Now Ember-roto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.50,0:12:10.50,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Nyaheat wants Mooland to see \N all the moves he knows!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.64,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.64,0:12:25.35,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Mooland’s punch caused Ember to \N become Great Blaze-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.77,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mooland’s training him!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.57,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Are you somewhere \N in this mist, Dad?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.57,0:12:41.41,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Father, it’s me, Lilie! \N I would very much like to see you...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.29,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Dad! If you’re there, \N then show yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.58,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.25,0:12:52.29,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,What do I do... \N I’m lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.92,0:12:54.88,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.14,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.18,0:13:10.35,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.90,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.48,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.82,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.78,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,You’ve grown so big, Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.12,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,And Amakaji, you’ve evolved \N into such a beauty!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.55,0:13:39.09,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.51,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry, Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.51,0:13:45.68,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m sorry I said I hated you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.39,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,It’s okay, Mao... \N It’s fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.23,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,But... But...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.07,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.19,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.65,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,That’s not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.74,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,You didn’t do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.95,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Listen, Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.33,0:14:12.58,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have said “I’m sorry”. \N What I should have said was...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.83,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.30,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.84,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you for being my daughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.89,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing me, \N your father and your brother...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.73,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,...so much love and happiness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.31,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.86,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking \N such good care of Amakaji.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.65,0:14:46.62,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you for doing such a great job \N looking after Aina Cafeteria.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.32,0:14:52.54,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank you for growing into \N such a cute, sincere girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.79,0:14:54.29,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Thank—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.62,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.09,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,I’m trying again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.64,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,So forget I said “I’m sorry” just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.14,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom... Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.56,0:15:18.15,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,...for being such a warm, \N kind mother to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.40,0:15:24.40,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you for making \N delicious food for me every day!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.82,0:15:30.41,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you... The walks we went on \N together were so much fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.87,0:15:37.67,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you for catching Amakaji \N so I wouldn’t be lonely!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.59,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.71,0:15:45.05,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you for \N giving birth to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.77,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Suiren, Kaki, Māmane!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.48,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Wait here for the others \N to come back!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.48,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Banbadoro!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.24,0:16:07.78,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It split just a little-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.45,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.09,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Nyaheat’s Ember has evolved \N into Great Blaze-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.42,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,You did it, Nyaheat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.64,0:16:37.10,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Banbadoro, wait here for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.49,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Kapu-Rehire!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.49,0:16:49.49,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I request that you give \N Lilie, Mao and Satoshi back to us!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.70,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Kapu-Rehire!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.96,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I beg of you! Bring them back \N while they {\i1}can{\i0} still return!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.34,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,This is no time to \N be idly dancing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.97,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,If you have no intention \N of letting them go...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.97,0:17:12.89,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Then I shall reclaim them \N by force, if I must!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.35,0:17:16.89,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Let us go, Golugh!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.31,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Luster Cannon! {This didn't register as a keyframe so I cut it down manually. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.24,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.62,Main,Sofu,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.87,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.21,0:17:45.29,Main,Sofu,0,0,0,,Hāpu'u. Kapu-Rehire has accepted you \N as the Island Queen of Poni Island.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.29,0:17:46.55,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Truthfully?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.51,Main,Sofu,0,0,0,,The Luster Cannon you fired \N to save your friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.51,0:17:55.80,Main,Sofu,0,0,0,,...moved Kapu-Rehire’s heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.43,Main,Sofu,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.81,0:18:02.73,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Kapu-Rehire, \N does that mean...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.11,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,The fog’s...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.62,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,Mao.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.21,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,I’m always with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.63,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.46,0:18:38.06,Main,Maomama,0,0,0,,You may not see me, but my heart is always \N with you, your father, and your brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.19,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.05,0:19:15.22,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Mooland!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.14,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,The mist is clearing-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.91,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.83,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Are we...?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.16,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Lilie! Gladio!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.12,Main,Lilie & Gladio,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.79,0:19:46.54,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.25,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,You’re okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.38,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,We were worried about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.38,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.96,0:19:53.46,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Mao{honorific note: Mao-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.26,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.26,0:19:59.18,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,That’s the Mythical Pokémon, \N Xiemi-roto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.30,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Xiemi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.81,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Xiemi. Gratitude Pokémon. \N Grass type.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.81,0:20:06.31,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,When it curls up its body, \N it looks like flowers.{This does not match its game dex entries. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.52,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,When Gracidea flowers \N are in season,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.82,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,it changes its form and flies off \N to deliver feelings of gratitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.40,0:20:17.07,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Will you stay with me \N until you fly off?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.70,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.37,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,Xiemi is so cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.37,0:20:26.46,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Suiren... I met Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.08,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,That’s great!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.38,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,We met Mooland!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.88,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,We...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.72,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Why didn’t Dad appear?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.68,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Is it not because he still lives?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.39,0:20:49.52,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,The fact that you could not see him, \N despite your strong desire to do so...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.44,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,...means that your father still lives...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.94,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,...somewhere within \N this unbelievably vast world.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.95,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Somewhere in this...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.20,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,...unbelievably vast world...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.99,0:21:02.53,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,We have to tell Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.70,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Yes! As quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.45,Main,Gladio,0,0,0,,Silvuddy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.21,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Gladio!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.83,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,When you next set foot on Poni Island, \N you may undertake my Grand Trial!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.09,0:21:15.59,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,Doesn’t that mean...?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.00,0:21:19.84,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Kapu-Rehire has accepted me \N as the Island Queen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.68,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,The explosive birth of \N an Island Queen!{Yes, it’s the exact same phrasing as in the title of M2. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.26,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Hāpu'u!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.60,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.72,0:21:29.18,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Well, then, please let me take your \N Grand Trial right now, Island Queen!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.18,0:21:32.15,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,Oh, Satoshi, \N you truly are a hasty one...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.15,0:21:36.32,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,The Grand Trial must wait until I have completed \N the ritual to become the Island Queen.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.32,0:21:38.19,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Okay, after that, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.32,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.82,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,In Kapu-Rehire’s mist, \N Mao met her mother...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.20,0:21:47.83,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,Nyaheat met his old master, Mooland.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.41,0:21:53.00,Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,With these precious experiences in their hearts, \N they now take another step towards the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.54,0:21:57.88,Main,Narrator,250,0,0,,And for Satoshi, the Poni Island \N Grand Trial awaits!
Comment: 10,0:21:59.46,0:21:59.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Comment: 10,0:23:20.46,0:23:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{PokéProblem - Answer}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.13,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.13,0:23:28.97,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,We went to Hāpu'u’s house!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.97,0:23:31.60,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,The Gratitude Pokémon Xiemi \N is a Grass type.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.60,0:23:33.27,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Apparently it can dissolve \N toxins in the air...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.27,0:23:37.48,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,...to instantly transform ruined land \N into a lush field of flowers!{Pearl Pokédex entry -Starfish}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.48,0:23:43.07,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Perhaps I was able to say “thank you” to Mom \N because of you, Xiemi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.45,0:23:53.50,Main,Hapu,0,0,0,,It appears you cannot sleep...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.20,0:23:55.58,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,You, too.
Comment: 10,0:24:00.50,0:24:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.13,0:24:03.96,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?! \N My research project isn’t finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.96,0:24:06.17,Main,Kaki,0,0,0,,It’s the final day already! \N What have you been doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.59,Main,Lilie,0,0,0,,You must stick to the plan \N with your research project!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.59,0:24:10.68,Main,Mamane,0,0,0,,It’s because you made \N the Grand Trial your project!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.68,0:24:11.76,Main,Mao,0,0,0,,Why not do something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.76,0:24:12.68,Main,Suiren,0,0,0,,A picture diary, for example?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.68,0:24:13.64,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.64,0:24:15.23,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Rotom, tell me the weather!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.23,0:24:16.52,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,It was sunny every day-roto.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.52,0:24:19.60,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,All right! I’m gonna draw our trip \N from the first day!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.60,0:24:22.27,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Next time, on Pocket Monsters Sun & Moon:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.27,0:24:25.40,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,An Island Queen is Born! \N Satoshi’s Grand Trial!!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:25.40,0:24:27.65,Main,Satoshi,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I don’t remember anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.45,Main,Rotom,0,0,0,,Just take Hāpu'u’s Grand Trial-roto.
